title: [1508521049] Ultimate Dinner Party Guide | 3 Courses in 30 Minutes - Gordon Ramsay
description:
Gordon shows Carol how to make 3 brilliantly simple dishes in just 30 minutes, serving up ceviche of salmon, chicken with crème fraiche and capers and a no-bake raspberry cheesecake. 
From Gordon Ramsay's The F Word
